tes every hour based on the premium between perpetual and spot prices. The exchange uses cross-margin by default, allowing traders to utilize their entire portfolio as collateral for TAO positions. Funding payments are automatically settled through Vertex's on-chain risk engine, ensuring transparent and verifiable transactions. The 0.02% maker rebate and 0.03% taker fee structure creates favorable conditions for high-frequency funding rate strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
